Cross-Referencing
This allows all elements within a Quarto document to be referenced from within the text, and then whenever you render the references are all updated automatically.



Type
Label Prefix
Reference Syntax




Figures
#| label: fig-
@fig-name


Tables
#| label: tbl-
@tbl-name


Equations
{#eq-name}
@eq-name


Sections
{#sec-name}
@sec-name
